  "text": "Numerous studies have described a key role for the transcription factor CREB (cAMP response element-binding protein) in neuroplasticity underlying learning and memory (Silva et al., 1998; [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Early work in Drosophila melanogaster showed that CREB is required for olfactory memory [CITATION_3] .",
